Package: kwt
Title: Tools for R at Kent Wildlife Trust
Version: 0.0.1.0016
Authors@R: c(
    person("Robbie", "Still", email = "robbie.still@kentwildlife.org.uk", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Euan", "Mckenzie", email = "euan.mckenzie@kentwildlife.org.uk", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides a basket of tools to make day-to-day work at Kent
    Wildlife Trust Group easier. This includes functions for working with
    the PostgreSQL database, as well as working with awkward spatial data
    types like grid references and postcodes.
